text: KLZL-LP (90.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to Ten Sleep, Wyoming, United States. The station is currently owned by Paint Rock Radio. ==See also== *List of community radio stations in the United States ==References== ==External links== * LZL-LP Category:Community radio stations in the United States LZL-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Wyoming
